snippet.title: Bailará (TB) | Dan Davison
snippet.description:
Bailará written by Dan Davison for TB, piano, guitar, and percussion. 

¡Bailará! is an original composition inspired by the flamenco tango style of Andalusia, Spain. Accompanied by piano, guitar, and percussion, this energetic work is an excellent choice for honor and festival choirs and for any occasion where a group wants to “bring the house down!”

Purchase the music: https://giamusic.com/resource/bailara-tb-printed-music-ww2093

Also available for TTBB voicing: https://giamusic.com/resource/bailara-ttbb-printed-music-ww2092
